{"type": "root", "attrs": {"tags": "rigidbodies", "icon": "PARTS/glue"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Glue Adjacent"], "extent": [0, 18]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Creates glue constraints between adjacent RBD objects."], "extent": [57, 119]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [119, 134], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool is similar to ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdglueobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Glue Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdglueobject"}, ", however instead of gluing all pieces to each other, only pieces that are adjacent are constrained. The Glue Adjacent tool creates four nodes: a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/constraintnetwork", "type": "link", "text": ["Constraint Network"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/constraintnetwork"}, " and a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/glueconrel", "type": "link", "text": ["Glue Constraint Relationship"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/glueconrel"}, " in the DOP network, and a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/connectadjacentpieces", "type": "link", "text": ["Connect Adjacent Pieces SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/connectadjacentpieces"}, " and an ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/attribwrangle", "type": "link", "text": ["Attrib Wrangle SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/attribwrangle"}, " in a new geometry object."], "extent": [134, 615]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [615, 621], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["This tool only works with the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rigidbodysolver", "type": "link", "text": ["Bullet Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rigidbodysolver"}, ". You can change the type of solver in the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Solver Engine"]}, " dropdown menu on the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rigidbodysolver", "type": "link", "text": ["Rigid Body Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rigidbodysolver"}, "."], "extent": [621, 828]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [828, 833], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["To remove the name prefix, you can change the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Object Names"]}, " parameter on the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/dopimport", "type": "link", "text": ["DOP Import SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/dopimport"}, " from ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Use Full Path to Object"]}, " to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Use DOP Object Name"]}, "."], "extent": [833, 1019]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["How to"], "extent": [1019, 1032], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Select any simulated objects you want to glue together."], "extent": [1032, 1092]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["In the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rigid Bodies"]}, " shelf tab, click ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "PARTS/glue", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/PARTS/glue"}, " ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Glue Adjacent"]}, "."], "extent": [1092, 1173]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["You will see a little black line appear between the objects once they are glued."], "extent": [1173, 1255]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/glueadjacent.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1255, 1295]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The tool will create glue constraints between selected objects that are close together. This lets you, for example, select a whole stack of boxes and use ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Glue Adjacent"]}, " to glue each box to its neighbors. If the objects you are trying to glue are too far apart, you can increase the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Search Radius"]}, " on the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/connectadjacentpieces", "type": "link", "text": ["Connect Adjacent Pieces SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/connectadjacentpieces"}, "."], "extent": [1295, 1668]}]}], "title": ["Glue Adjacent"], "summary": ["Creates glue constraints between adjacent RBD objects."]}